TECHNICAL DISCLAIMERS:
=====================

1. Amazon Alexa Integration:
   This software requires Amazon Alexa Skills Kit and AWS Lambda services.
   Amazon's terms of service and privacy policies apply to Alexa integration.

2. Performance Requirements:
   Real-time audio processing performance depends on network connectivity,
   AWS Lambda cold starts, and Echo device capabilities.

3. BEA Technology Dependencies:
   Some features require proprietary BEA algorithms. Commercial use may
   require separate licensing for full functionality.

4. Audio Processing:
   Audio enhancement results may vary based on source material, device
   limitations, and processing constraints.

